# WASM Providers (Standard)

- One directory per provider under `plugins/wasm/<name>/`
- Required files: `provider.json` + `provider.wasm`
- Exports: `malloc`, `Send` (see `pkg/plugin/wasm/abi.go`)
- Host imports: `herald.log`, `herald.get_context`, `herald.http_fetch` (SDK: `plugins/sdk/herald/`)
- `permissions` in provider.json required for outbound HTTP (`network:https://...`)
- Restart **both** API and Worker after adding/changing plugins

Full guide: `docs/WASM_PROVIDERS.md`
